{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778598077891,"sessionID":"ses_1e3617951ffeRrEoaJkTlyk1Ha","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"chatcmpl-tool-90d7f9ace225b66d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"## Summary of Changes\n- Removed the `is_a` relationship from `thoracic dorsal root ganglion` (UBERON:0002835) to `thoracic ganglion` (UBERON:0000961).\n- Renamed `thoracic ganglion` (UBERON:0000961) to `thoracic paravertebral ganglion` to accurately reflect its nature as a paravertebral ganglion and avoid confusion with other ganglia in the thorax.\n\n## Rationale\nDorsal root ganglia are not paravertebral/sympathetic ganglia. Therefore, the `thoracic dorsal root ganglion` should not be a subclass of `thoracic ganglion` (now `thoracic paravertebral ganglion`). The renaming of `thoracic ganglion` to `thoracic paravertebral ganglion` provides better anatomical precision.\n\n## Validation\n- Verified the original relationship and name in `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n- Used `obo-checkout.pl` and `obo-checkin.pl` for editing.\n- Reserialized the ontology using `robot convert`.\n","filePath":"PR_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778598077885,"end":1778598077890}},"id":"prt_e1cb2f090001hJqpPMfgO6jHqw","sessionID":"ses_1e3617951ffeRrEoaJkTlyk1Ha","messageID":"msg_e1cb2ea70001bEZe3W41UZl2SN"}}
